 <span data-ttu-id="722d4-106">您將新增<xref:System.Windows.VisualState>藉由設定控制`VisualStateManager.VisualStateGroups`附加在控制項上的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-106">You add <xref:System.Windows.VisualState> to a control by setting the `VisualStateManager.VisualStateGroups` attached property on the control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-107">您將狀態互斥彼此在同一個<xref:System.Windows.VisualStateGroup>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-107">You put states that are mutually exclusive to each other in the same <xref:System.Windows.VisualStateGroup>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-108">例如，<xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>有兩個<xref:System.Windows.VisualStateGroup>物件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-108">For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> has two <xref:System.Windows.VisualStateGroup> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-109">其中包含狀態， `Normal`， `MouseOver`， `Pressed`，和`Disabled`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-109">One contains the states, `Normal`, `MouseOver`, `Pressed`, and `Disabled`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-110">另一個包含州`Checked`， `UnChecked`，和`Indeterminate`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-110">The other contains the states, `Checked`, `UnChecked`, and `Indeterminate`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-111"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox>可能處於狀態`MouseOver`並`UnChecked`在此同時，但不是能在`MouseOver`和`Pressed`一次的狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-111">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox> can be in states `MouseOver` and `UnChecked` at the same time, but it cannot be in the `MouseOver` and `Pressed` states at the same time.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="722d4-112">雖然您可以新增<xref:System.Windows.VisualState>物件的任何項目，是特別有用的方式，讓他人以重新定義的視覺行為<xref:System.Windows.Controls.Control>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-112">Although you can add <xref:System.Windows.VisualState> objects to any element, they are a particularly useful way to enable others to redefine the visual behavior of a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Control>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-113">如果您建立使用自訂控制項<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>，您可以指定哪些狀態控制項，可以藉由新增在成為<xref:System.Windows.TemplateVisualStateAttribute>在其類別定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-113">If you create a custom control that uses a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>, you can specify which states that control can be in by adding a <xref:System.Windows.TemplateVisualStateAttribute> on its class definition.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-114">然後建立新的人<xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate>針對您的控制項可以新增<xref:System.Windows.VisualState>物件至範本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-114">Then anyone who creates a new <xref:System.Windows.Controls.ControlTemplate> for your control can add <xref:System.Windows.VisualState> objects to the template.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-115"><xref:System.Windows.TemplateVisualStateAttribute>可讓設計工具，例如 Expression Blend，來公開控制項的狀態。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-115">The <xref:System.Windows.TemplateVisualStateAttribute> enables designer tools, such as Expression Blend, to expose the control's states.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722d4-116">具有相同的狀態<xref:System.Windows.TemplateVisualStateAttribute.GroupName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬於相同<xref:System.Windows.VisualStateGroup>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722d4-116">States with the same <xref:System.Windows.TemplateVisualStateAttribute.GroupName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> belong in the same <xref:System.Windows.VisualStateGroup>.</span></span>  
  
